<p class="eyebrow">Company</p>
<h1>Wholesale communications for teams that need engineering depth.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel builds and operates communications services for developers, telecom engineers, service providers, and businesses that need transparent pricing, practical migration paths, and support from people who understand the network.</p>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel has built networks for national carriers on a consultation basis — that engineering experience is embedded in every product we ship and every customer we support.</p>

<section class="section-block" data-section-type="positioning">
	<h2>What VoiceTel does</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Programmable Voice</strong> — <a href="/voiceml/">VoiceML</a>-compatible call control, signed webhooks, recordings, conferences, queues, streams, and <a href="/voiceml/migrate/">migration guidance</a>.</li>
		<li><strong>Wholesale network services</strong> — <a href="/voice/">Voice</a> origination and termination, <a href="/sip-trunking/">SIP trunking</a>, <a href="/numbers/">numbers</a>, porting, emergency-service configuration, and caller identity services (<a href="/caller-lookup/">Caller Lookup</a>, <a href="/carrier-lookup/">Carrier Lookup</a>).</li>
		<li><strong>Application messaging</strong> — <a href="/messaging/">SMS and MMS</a> transport with A2P 10DLC support, delivery visibility, and high-volume planning.</li>
		<li><strong>Business calling</strong> — <a href="/pbx/">Hosted PBX</a>, <a href="/phone/applications/">VoiceTel Phone</a>, and <a href="/sdn/">SDN appliance</a> options for organizations that want VoiceTel to operate more of the stack.</li>
	</ul>
</section>

<section class="section-block">
	<h2>Company</h2>
	<p>United Internet Services d.b.a. VoiceTel was incorporated in the State of New Jersey in 1999. It is licensed with the FCC as a Non-Interconnected VoIP Provider and a Competitive Local Exchange Carrier (CLEC). FCC Filer ID <a href="https://apps.fcc.gov/cgb/form499/499detail.cfm?FilerNum=829231">829231</a>. Robocall Mitigation Database ID <a href="https://fccprod.servicenowservices.com/rmd">RMD0004909</a>. OCN <strong>470J</strong>.</p>
</section>

